  "prompt": "When is surge pricing on Uber generally in effect in Sarasota and how high does it go?",
  "response": "Surge pricing on Uber typically occurs during periods of high demand, such as during special events, holidays, weekends, or adverse weather conditions. In Sarasota, like in many other locations, surge pricing can vary significantly based on local events and times of day. \n\nThe exact multiplier for surge pricing can fluctuate, sometimes ranging from 1.2x to 2.5x the standard fare, but it can go even higher during peak demand times. It\u2019s best to check the Uber app for real-time pricing in your area, as it will provide the most accurate information regarding surge pricing at any given moment.",
